Interactive OpenID Connect (OIDC) authentication backend for OPNsense.
Provides an Authorization Code + PKCE browser flow and maps resulting
ID token claims to an OPNsense user identity for GUI login.

Features:
 - Authorization Code + PKCE
 - Claim mapping to username
 - (Planned) group / role filtering
 - JWKS caching and JWT validation

Limitations (initial version):
 - No silent token refresh
 - Single provider per auth server entry
 - Auto user provisioning optional future feature
